---
title: BBQ Rubbed Chicken and Picnic Broccoli Salad with Creamy Dill Dressing and Cranberries
description: Unbelievably simple and packed with flavour, this dish brings summer to your plate. Nothing like sweet, smoky barbecue flavour on juicy chicken thighs and a creamy, dreamy broccoli salad to pair alongside!
